Rise of the Planet of the Apes;;77;;82;;PG-13;;Will Rodman (James Franco), a scientist in San Francisco, is experimenting with a drug that he hopes will cure his father's (John Lithgow) Alzheimer's disease. After his work is deemed a failure, Will becomes the guardian of Caesar, an infant chimp who was exposed in-utero to Will's drug. Caesar displays unusual intelligence, and Will decides to continue his experiments secretly. But as Caesar's intellect and abilities grow, he comes to represent a threat to man's dominion over Earth.;;Action,Adventure,Sci-fi;;Rupert Wyatt;;2011;;James Franco,Freida Pinto,John Lithgow,Brian Cox,Tom Felton,David Oyelowo,Andy Serkis,Tyler Labine,Jamie Harris,David Hewlett,Ty Olsson,Madison Bell,Makena Joy;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rise_of_the_planet_of_the_apes